Download:
Crimson Editor - http://www.crimsoneditor.com/english/download.html
zmac - Z-80 Macro Cross Assembler - http://48k.ca/zmac.zip
Tera Term - https://github.com/TeraTermProject/teraterm/releases

Configuration:
Crimson:
Goto 'Tools > Prefrences > Categories > Tools > User Tools' and do as per instructions bellow (please see the image 'Crimson configuration.jpg').

User Tool		Hot Key
 - ZMAC			F5
 
Menu Text:		 - ZMAC
Command:		C:\zmac\zmac-pgr\zmac.exe
Argument:		$(FileName) -c -j -n --oo hex,lst --od c:\zmac\zout	
Initial Dir:	$(FileDir)
Hot Key:		F5

My zmac folder structure:
zmac
 |___my-asm (my asm programs)
 |___scr (zmac source)
 |___zmac-pgr (zmac executable)
 |___zout (.lst and .hex files)

Tera Term:
Speed: 115200 bps
Data: 8 bit
Parity: none
Stop bits: 1 bit
Flow Control: RTS/CTS

